          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/rollingge/" class=" " title="如林">如林</a>
                (林无静树 川无停流)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="41255634">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">“就是罗斯福一把火烧了国会，我们也会大声欢呼说，‘好哇，火到底点着啦！’”</span>
